Name: Terrorist Elimination
About the game: GamePlay: Purchase guns and ammo in the store, kill terrorist in each stage/level to progress further in the game. Features: • FPS: Terrorist Elimination is a first person shooter • Guns: M40A3, Dragunov, M16, AK47, Benelli M4, MP5, AEK-971, HKG36K, and more! • Levels: Each level has 3 stages that need to be cleared out before unlocking more levels • $Cash: Used to purchase guns and ammo in the store • Loot: Terrorist guns, such as an ak-47 and the rpg can only be found in combat. Cash$ can also be found in combat. • HardCore: No save/load, no hp or armor ui, and no checkpoints.
